{
  "texts": [
    "[17] Recently, some exploration has been made into LLM performance in the eld of pediatrics.",
    "Jason Holmes et al.",
    "evaluated LLMs in highly standardized professional scenarios in pediatric ophthalmology.This was followed by a further study by Zhi Wei Lim et al.",
    "assessing different LLMs response capabilities in more realistic scenarios of myopia management.",
    "However, studies evaluating LLMs response capabilities in the eld of adolescent growth and development have not been found to date."
  ]
}